title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“No matter where you live in Cleveland, we're only twenty minutes from downtown.” [From a commercial on WVAB-TV, Cleveland, 27 August 1982. Submitted by Dr. Dorothy Branson, Columbus, Ohio.]
